{"tid":1074031,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"韶 山 遊 客 喜 獲 毛 主 席 接 見","createTime":"2019-03-23T06:10:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-23T06:57:02.000Z","uid":19408,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"f0ae24626e00caf63a88c8f54ff07e8c5e666c80","tid":1074031,"uid":19408,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-23T06:10:51.000Z","msg":"突發！湖南高速一旅遊大巴起火 已致26死28傷！<br />\n<br />\n黑龍江晨報 2019-03-23 07:01<br />\n記者23日從湖南省委宣傳部獲悉，3月22日19時15分許，湖南常長高速西往東方向119KM+655M處（常德市漢壽縣太子廟服務區附近），一輛從河南鄭州開出的柴油旅遊大巴豫AZ8999（機動車所有人為河南迅馳汽車旅遊服務有限公司）突然起火。<br />\n<br />\n該車核載59人，實載56人，其中乘客53人、司機2人、導遊1人。事故造成26人死亡，28人受傷（其中5人重傷），2名司機已被控制。受傷人員已妥善安排在當地3家醫院接受救治。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n事故發生後，湖南省委省政府迅速組織省、市、縣三級公安、應急、衛健等部門趕赴現場救援處置，全力搶救傷員，做好善後工作。河南省派員正在趕赴湖南開展相關工作。<br />\n<br />\n躲過一劫的幸存者薛先生向記者介紹，車輛由開封始發，目的地是<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">韶山</span></span>。大巴起火部位是後部。「後面先燒起來的，不一會兒整個車都燒了起來。」<br />\n<br />\n事故原因正在調查之中。<br />\n<br />\n來源： 新華社"},{"pid":"b9bca9ca9840de56910a48c567b3144d1eab7430","tid":1074031,"uid":98386,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-23T06:11:53.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">蒙毛寵召</span></span>"},{"pid":"bd2c1306658a03c198f71a3ec7c0723673655d0a","tid":1074031,"uid":133519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-23T06:13:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />韶山好嘢 多謝韶山<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64d96b5c0fc4e7d9873304bd8c63fa61948eb7c2","tid":1074031,"uid":155095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-23T06:15:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20180519/31eb90ff65d14ee5ba86aaf7a59e9ff0.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2F5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com%2Fimages%2F20180519%2F31eb90ff65d14ee5ba86aaf7a59e9ff0.jpeg&h=3a5502bf&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a2b387d3b9b242f4ca25fc8a08530ab39c84f4b5","tid":1074031,"uid":28195,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-23T06:18:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wCNV1fP.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwCNV1fP.png&h=13f1c941&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5666ee08a36f72a41c2a4284ca1625f8c11c18d6","tid":1074031,"uid":19408,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-23T06:57:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}